Introduction

Jo Eun Ae, known as D.ana is a South-Korean singer and dancer, best known for being member of the now disbanded girl group Sonamoo under TS Entertainment.

She also participated in KBS's Idol Drama Operation Team, along with the other idols and created a project girl group "Girl Next Door".
